## ⏱️ Quick Start Guide

1.  **Launch:** Open the [Live Demo Link](https://trisha227.github.io/Smart-Volunteer-Resource-Allocation/) or open `index.html` locally.
2.  **Digitize:** Go to the **"Ingest Data"** tab. Upload an image of a survey or paste raw field notes.
3.  **Analyze:** Click **"Analyze with Gemini"**. The system will structure the data and calculate the priority.
4.  **Match:** Head to the **"Smart Matcher"**, select the new task, and click **"Find Best Matches"**.
5.  **Assign:** Click **"Assign"** to notify the volunteer and update the live map.

